title: ASME 2013 Standards Boiler and Pressure Vessel Code
description:
ASME 2013 Standards Boiler and Pressure Vessel Code (Sections 2, 5, 8, 9)

The BPVC (Boiler and Pressure Vessel Code) provides rules for the design, fabrication, installation, inspection, care, and use of boilers, pressure vessels, and nuclear components. The code also includes standards on materials, welding and brazing procedures and qualifications, nondestructive examination, and nuclear in-service inspection
